2025 PMSL CSA Fall Season ko Official Broadcast ma swagat cha ‚Äì Grand Finals! üëë

It all comes down to this‚Äîthe final battleground jaha legacy haru forge hunchan ra  matra euta team le trophy uthaune cha.

üî• Chaos. Clutch. History. Sab huncha.
Yehi ho moment jasko lagi pura region wait gardai thiyo‚Äîwho will rise as the PMSL CSA Fall Champion of 2025? üèÜ

Today, the SMASH RULE takes over:

üß® What is the SMASH RULE?

1Ô∏è‚É£ At the end of Day 2, the overall leader‚Äôs total points +10 will become the Match Point threshold.
2Ô∏è‚É£ Today is the day! Once a team reaches or exceeds the Match Point threshold, they must win a Chicken Dinner in a subsequent match to be crowned champions
3Ô∏è‚É£ Be the Champions! ‚Äì If no team meets both conditions by the end of all 18 matches, the team with the highest total points will be declared the champion.

Everything is on the line ‚ÄîTrophy, legacy, and one final zone.

üí∞Total Prize Pool: $200,000

OSR Digital is one of the largest digital and physical (CD, VCD, DVD) movie distribution companies in Nepal. snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Hindi Success Trailer | Rishab Shetty, Rukmini Vasanth | Hombale films
snippet.description:
From Hombale Films ‚Äî the makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar ‚Äî and the visionary, National Award‚Äìwinning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies and a saga that will echo through generations.

snippet.title: Ujan Shakya - Baby (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
MEY STUDIO & VISIONS MEDIA PRODUCTION
PRESENTS

BABY by Ujan Shakya || New Newari Song || New Nepal Bhasa Song || New Nepali Song

"Baby" explores the theme of love. It depicts the concept of love at first sight through a narrative that combines imagination and emotion. The piece is characterized as an emotional afrobeat , featuring a blend of Newari instruments.

snippet.title: Andhra King Taluka Teaser | Ram Pothineni | Upendra | Mahesh Babu P | Bhagyashri Borse
snippet.description:
Presenting the Energetic teaser of #AndhraKingTaluka 

Andhra King Taluka - A BIOPIC OF A FAN is a Telugu Film starring Ram Pothineni, Upendra and Bhagyashri Borse. The film is written and directed by Mahesh Babu P and produced by Naveen Yerneni, Y. Ravi Shankar under Mythri Movie Makers. Music is by Vivek & Mervin. The film brings untold emotions between a fan and a superstar onto the big screens on 28th November worldwide.

snippet.description:
The Top 8 teams from the Semi Finals and Top 8 teams from the Survival Stage are set to battle across 3 intense days of high-stakes BGMI action. The competition is fierce, the pressure is real, and only one team will rise above the rest.

The team that finishes at the top of the leaderboard will earn a slot at the global stage, as the journey to go Beyond Limits reaches its peak!

Madkings
mysterious4 Esports

iQOO 8BIT

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

snippet.title: Tumse Behtar | Varun D, Janhvi K, Sanya M, Rohit S | Tanishk B, Arijit S, Manoj M | SSKTK
snippet.description:
You‚Äôve seen them dance, you‚Äôve seen them fall in love, now witness the heartbreak when love gets intertwined! Presenting ‚ÄòTumse Behtar‚Äô from ‚ÄòSunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari‚Äô, starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra and Rohit Saraf. Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and written by Manoj Muntashir, this beautiful song is sung by Arijit Singh.

#TumseBehtar #ArijitSingh #TanishkBagchi #SSKTK

Music Composer: Tanishk Bagchi
Lyricist: Manoj Muntashir
Singer: Arijit Singh
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi & Krishna Kishor
Woodwinds: Nikhil Ram
Keys: Navneeth, Anoop, Melvin
Male Chorus: Rahul, Sanjay, Abijith, Aston
Female Chorus: Kamalaja, Fathima, Nayansi, Aarthi
Arijit Singh's Vocals Recorded by: Sukanto Singha
Arijit Singh‚Äôs Recordings Managed by: Ashish Biswal
Mixed and Mastered by: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani and Varun Dhawan
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Lyrics:
Tumhara-mera milna likha to hoga kahin
Naseebon ka sitara, mila to hoga Kahin

Na Jane kyun ae humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Raaton me, bina tumhare ghabrayein, ghabraayein
Khwaabon me, milo agar khush ho jaayein ho jaayein

Chain ho tum aaram ho shayad
Koi sukoon ki shaam ho shayad
Khushi kahoon ya dil ki tasalli
Kya tumhein doon main naam

Kitabein dekhi saari, mili na koi shaayri
Tareefein karoon kaise, yahi hai muhskil meri

Na Jane kyun a humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi
Jo daraeyin wo hawayein gham ki, tham jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Dekho na ye kamaal hua hai
Aesa dil ka haal hua hai
Dil mera tere itar me dooba
Jaise koi roomal hua hai

Aesi hai khwahish dil me mere
Jaane mujhe sab naam se tere
Aesi diwangi pahle nahin thee
Haal ye pichhle saal hua hai

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Koi nahin tumse behtar, tumse pyaara
Tumse zyaada mera koi nahin!

Step into the world of resonant romance with Alka Yagnik's enchanting voice in the unforgettable track 'Ikrar Ho Na Jaye' from the movie Zinda Dil. This soulful melody from the early 2000s is sure to rekindle the season of love in your hearts. Let the silky timbre of Alka Yagnik, the queen of romantic numbers, transport you to an era where music was emotionally stirring and purely heartfelt. Dive deep into the pool of nostalgia and let the magic of the song wrap you in its romantic embrace.

Ikrar Ho Na Jaye



Credits :

Song: Ikrar Ho Na Jaye
Album: Zinda Dil
Artist: Alka Yagnik
Music Director: Nadeem-Shravan
Lyricist: Sameer 


Which song made you fall in love with Alka Yagnik's voice all over again? Comment down below. Don't forget to hit the like button if you enjoyed the song and subscribe to our channel for more melodious treats like this. Let the magic of music live on...

snippet.title: Sabailai
snippet.description:
Song Credits
Purna Rai and Dajubhaiharu
recording - Ashish Pathak
mix and master - Thile Thakali
edited - NP Films 


This song is a heartfelt dedication to all the well-wishers and supporters of my music from audiences at shows to Nepalis at home and across the world. It reflects my deep gratitude for the love and encouragement that have carried me and my band throughout our journey. Filled with happiness and thankfulness, the song also expresses my commitment to continue creating music, songs that honor my people‚Äôs unwavering support and celebrate the special musical connection we share.
